492
00:40:40,679 --> 00:40:42,480
and taken to a hospital.

493
00:40:42,610 --> 00:40:43,749
- The dead arsonist... - Coming through.

494
00:40:43,750 --> 00:40:46,149
turned out to be the culprit...

495
00:40:46,150 --> 00:40:48,149
- Can someone help? - of the studio apartment fire...

496
00:40:48,150 --> 00:40:50,848
- One, two, three. - that killed a pregnant woman...

497
00:40:50,849 --> 00:40:53,488
as well as the Seongbuk-dong incident,

498
00:40:53,489 --> 00:40:55,360
which is truly shocking.

499
00:41:04,269 --> 00:41:05,469
Yeon Woo.

500
00:41:06,070 --> 00:41:07,070
No.

501
00:41:07,599 --> 00:41:08,869
Yeon Woo!

502
00:41:15,010 --> 00:41:16,178
Yeon Woo.

503
00:41:16,179 --> 00:41:17,550
- So Jin. - Yeon Woo.

504
00:41:18,150 --> 00:41:21,179
Yeon Woo. Is he okay?

505
00:41:22,380 --> 00:41:23,849
He's in surgery.

506
00:41:25,650 --> 00:41:26,789
Surgery?

507
00:41:27,760 --> 00:41:29,460
You should stay in bed.

508
00:41:37,469 --> 00:41:38,630
Yeon Woo.

509
00:41:39,239 --> 00:41:40,440
Yeon Woo.

510
00:41:41,500 --> 00:41:42,500
No.

511
00:41:46,179 --> 00:41:49,210
Yeon Woo.

512
00:41:50,349 --> 00:41:52,780
Please. No.

513
00:41:53,280 --> 00:41:54,820
Yeon Woo.

514
00:41:56,019 --> 00:41:57,550
Yeon Woo.

515
00:41:59,460 --> 00:42:02,730
Please. Yeon Woo.

516
00:42:03,889 --> 00:42:06,630
(Operating Center)

517
00:42:08,630 --> 00:42:09,999
Are you Sim Yeon Woo's family?

518
00:42:10,000 --> 00:42:12,799
Yes. He's okay, isn't he?

519
00:42:12,800 --> 00:42:14,839
The other burns weren't serious,

520
00:42:14,840 --> 00:42:16,169
but his right arm's was bad.

521
00:42:16,170 --> 00:42:18,210
His muscles and ligaments were badly damaged.

522
00:42:18,639 --> 00:42:21,009
We tried to preserve them through emergency surgery,

523
00:42:21,010 --> 00:42:22,379
but we must see how things go.

524
00:42:22,380 --> 00:42:24,549
The burn and inflammation must go down...

525
00:42:24,550 --> 00:42:26,178
if we're to transplant ligaments or skin.

526
00:42:26,179 --> 00:42:28,280
Did he regain consciousness?

527
00:42:28,420 --> 00:42:31,089
His oxygen saturation dropped due to smoke inhalation,

528
00:42:31,090 --> 00:42:32,559
so he's on a ventilator.

529
00:42:33,159 --> 00:42:36,090
People usually wake up as their lungs clear.

530
00:42:36,230 --> 00:42:38,829
But not Mr. Sim, which is odd.

531
00:43:18,300 --> 00:43:19,340
So Jin.

532
00:43:22,239 --> 00:43:25,309
You can go home tomorrow if you feel well enough.

533
00:43:25,710 --> 00:43:28,408
I must go to the police station to give a statement.

534
00:43:28,409 --> 00:43:29,948
This is red snow crab porridge.

535
00:43:29,949 --> 00:43:32,449
Eat this if you don't like the hospital food.

536
00:43:32,510 --> 00:43:34,018
Don't worry about me...

537
00:43:34,019 --> 00:43:36,750
and go home from the police station.

538
00:43:37,150 --> 00:43:40,059
A Ri will come tomorrow with some clothes.

539
00:43:41,960 --> 00:43:44,558
Both you and Yeon Woo are in hospital.

540
00:43:44,559 --> 00:43:46,630
Do you think I can sleep well at home?

541
00:43:48,599 --> 00:43:51,469
Ms. Jang said she'd come by tomorrow.

542
00:43:51,869 --> 00:43:53,840
